Validate profile

Usage: wheelctl profile validate [OPTIONS] <PATH>

Arguments:
  <PATH>  Profile path

Options:
  -d, --detailed    Show detailed validation info
      --json        Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -v, --verbose...  Verbose logging
  -h, --help        Print help
